data.description: Welcome to 8800 Old Mill Ln, Spotsylvania, VA 22551—a charming single-family rambler that seamlessly blends quiet country living with conveniences. This 1,639 square foot home has 3 bedrooms and 2.0 bathrooms, providing a comfortable, one-level living space. Recent updates have enhanced the functionality and style of this residence, including a newer roof, HVAC system, and hot water heater, ensuring peace of mind and energy efficiency. The kitchen has been upgraded with brand-new countertops, adding a touch of contemporary style and functionality to the heart of the home. Fresh paint throughout the entire house enhances the bright and welcoming atmosphere. Adding to the square footage of this home is a very spacious, light-filled, sunroom, a perfect retreat for relaxation or entertaining guests. From the sunroom, venture out onto the large deck, ideal for enjoying the beauty of the expansive, flat, and cleared lot. This property offers ample outdoor space, providing endless possibilities for family activities, gardening, or simply enjoying the serene surroundings. Additional features include a detached garage for secure parking or storage, a circular driveway for convenient access, and a chicken coop for those interested in farm-fresh eggs or a small-scale hobby farm. This home at 8800 Old Mill Ln is more than just a residence; it's a lifestyle. Experience the joy and convenience of of spacious one-level living areas, and the freedom to enjoy the outdoors on this large and inviting property. Embrace the tranquility of the countryside while still enjoying the convenience of being close to major commuting routes and urban centers. This is an opportunity to make cherished memories in a home that effortlessly combines comfort, style, and the beauty of nature.
